extendedInfo.description: Byrne Dairy has been around since 1933 serving you the freshest milk products from local farms. With the Byrne Dairy app, you can look locate one of our 53 Central New York locations, look up gas price and receive great deals! FIND A STORE & DIRECTIONS Find the closest Byrne Dairy store and get directions from your current location. Find nearby stores based on city and state, or zip code. GAS PRICE:Get real-time gas information for Byrne Dairy Stores. PROMOTION ALERTS Signup to receive alerts about special promotions and deals available at Byrne Dairy Stores. SEND FEEDBACK How was your Byrne Dairy experience? Tell us by submitting your comments directly from your phone.

reviews.title: Great milk!
reviews.comment: Best milk I\'ve found in upstate NY, ice cream is pretty good, but is a little airy and needs more & bigger chunks.
reviews.author: A Google User

reviews.title: Great appp but...
reviews.comment: Only issues I have are that there aren\'t many deals, they aren\'t that great, not all byrne dairy\'s have the deals and the deals don\'t change very often. Also, once u use one, you can\'t use it again. I still rate 4 stars because hey, even with all that, it\'s free and the coupons save you money.

reviews.title: Not bad just not great
reviews.comment: I like this app but there aren\'t to many deals and they don\'t really change. The deals, when they have new ones are pretty good though. So not bad, just not as great as I want it to be.

reviews.title: Great app
reviews.comment: Love the app, especially the deal coupons....when the cashier knows how to use them.  Had both cashiers at a local store look at me like i had two heads when i told them i had a coupon on my phone. I think they thought i was from the future- they didn\'t even know the app & coupons existed.  Like i said, great app but staff training on how to use it should be in order.
